<div class="recycle-about">
<h2>Dynamix File Recycle Bin / 文件回收站</h2>
<p>
    <b>Version / 版本:</b> <?= htmlspecialchars($version, ENT_QUOTES) ?>
</p>

<h3>EN — What it does</h3>
<ul>
    <li>Adds a "Move to Recycle Bin" button to every row in the Dynamix File Manager (Browse page).</li>
    <li>Files and folders are moved to a per-volume <code>.RecycleBin</code> directory instead of being deleted.</li>
    <li>Supports verified internal <code>/mnt/disk*</code> data drives and local ZFS datasets.</li>
    <li>User shares, cache/pools, UD/external mounts, remote paths, USB/removable media, and the Unraid boot device are rejected after click with an explicit reason.</li>
    <li>Settings provides a validated switch for every currently supported disk or dataset.</li>
    <li>Open <b>Settings → Dynamix File Recycle Bin</b> to enable, configure maintenance, log level, history recording, and language.</li>
    <li>Open <b>Tools → Recycle Bin</b> to browse, restore, or permanently purge items.</li>
</ul>

<h3>中文 — 功能说明</h3>
<ul>
    <li>在 Dynamix File Manager（Browse 页面）的每一行上添加"移入回收站"按钮。</li>
    <li>文件与文件夹会被移动到对应卷的 <code>.RecycleBin</code> 目录，而不是被永久删除。</li>
    <li>支持经过验证的内部 <code>/mnt/disk*</code> 数据盘和本地 ZFS dataset。</li>
    <li>用户共享、缓存池、UD/外置挂载、远程路径、USB/可移动介质和 Unraid 启动盘都会在点击后给出明确拒绝原因。</li>
    <li>设置页会为当前受支持的每个磁盘或 dataset 提供经过后端验证的管理开关。</li>
    <li>打开 <b>Settings → Dynamix File Recycle Bin</b> 启用插件并配置维护、日志级别、历史记录和语言。</li>
    <li>打开 <b>Tools → Recycle Bin</b> 浏览、还原或永久删除回收站内容。</li>
</ul>

<h3>Recycle bin location / 回收站位置</h3>
<table class="settings">
    <tr><th>Source path / 原路径</th><th>Recycle location / 回收站位置</th></tr>
    <tr><td><code>/mnt/disk1/Movies/x.mkv</code></td><td><code>/mnt/disk1/.RecycleBin/Movies/x.mkv</code></td></tr>
    <tr><td><code>/mnt/tank/photos/2025/a.jpg</code></td><td><code>/mnt/tank/.RecycleBin/photos/2025/a.jpg</code></td></tr>
</table>

<h3>Security / 安全</h3>
<p>
    All write operations require an admin session. Paths are normalised and
    confined to their original volume. CSRF is verified by Unraid's own
    <code>auto_prepend</code>; the plugin never re-implements it.
    &nbsp;|&nbsp;
    所有写操作均要求管理员登录；路径会被规范化并限制在原卷内；CSRF 由 Unraid 官方
    <code>auto_prepend</code> 校验，插件不重复实现。
</p>

<h3>Diagnostics / 诊断日志</h3>
<p>
    Runtime / 运行日志：<code>/usr/local/emhttp/state/plugins/dynamix.file.recycle/logs/dynamix.file.recycle.log</code><br>
    Persistent errors / 持久错误：<code>/boot/config/plugins/dynamix.file.recycle/logs/audit.log</code>
</p>
